**Team Charter**
    • Values: Speeding the response time to customers , solving their problems at the time , sharing issues with them.
    • Communication guideline :Making a time for daily questionnaires between the team .	
    • Fun Events : Celebration for every delivered project , Monthly outing .
    • Norms: Defining working and break hours , Focus on employees ethics .
    • Meeting guideline : Setup meetings on the calendar , notify employees with meetings time .
    • Making a discussion before taking decision .
       
